                    <para>
                      <text>The provision of <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Part 4</citation></changeable> of the Search and Surveillance Powers Act <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">2008</citation></changeable> apply in respect of the power conferred by subsection (1)(d).</text>
