                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">6</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>Despite <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">subsection (5)</citation></changeable>, <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">sections 121(2), 127(5)(e), and 128, and subparts 5 and 7 of Part 4</citation></changeable> of the Search and Surveillance Powers Act <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">2008</citation></changeable> do not apply to any goods forfeit to the Crown under section 225 of this Act.</text>
